title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 7-5.9 - Overnight transient occupancy
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 7-5.9 - Overnight transient occupancy

State Regulations

Structures at an agricultural fairground not meeting the definition of a camping unit which are available for overnight transient occupancy shall meet the requirements of Subpart 7-1 of this Part. Notes
